      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing straightforward transportation. The engine and transmission are in good working order, and the car drives reliably; however, please be aware that there are noticeable cosmetic imperfections, including some scratches on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained to ensure safety and functionality, making it a solid choice for a driver who prioritizes utility over a pristine appearance.",
