    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a car to tinker with? This vehicle is a great candidate for someone who loves a hands-on approach! While it currently needs significant mechanical attention and shows heavy wear inside and out, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost. It's rough around the edges, but with some dedicated TLC, it could be back on the road in no time!",
