    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior is immaculate, featuring pristine upholstery and a cabin that still smells new. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as intended and a comprehensive service history confirming its meticulous upkeep. Buyers can expect a top-tier vehicle that requires absolutely no investment or attention, offering a like-new experience in every regard.",
      "price": 48000.0,
